definitions.definition: An inner suburb of Bristol , England , between Clifton , Redland and St Pauls ( OS grid ref ST5874 ) .
A small village and civil parish (without a council) in Newark and Sherwood district, Nottinghamshire , England ( OS grid ref SK7947 ) .
